de.iabg.mode
Class MassMatrixMap

java.lang.Object
  javax.swing.AbstractListModel
      de.iabg.mode.MassMatrixMap
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.ComboBoxModel, javax.swing.ListModel
public class MassMatrixMap
extends javax.swing.AbstractListModel
implements javax.swing.ComboBoxModel

This ComboBoxModel is backed by a LinkedHashMap since there are several instances where it is convenient to have this combination. The type of elements stored in the map are MassMatrix objects. The methods in this class simply wrap those in LinkedHashMap or they use the map to implement the methods declared in ComboBoxModel.

September 12, 2008
